title: FSIS Issues Public Health Alert for Expansion of Imported Canadian Raw Boneless Beef Trim from XL Foods-092112
summary: WASHINGTON, September 21, 2012 - The U.S. Department of Agriculture's Food Safety and Inspection Service (FSIS) is announcing additional information related to the Sept. 20 Public Health Alert for raw boneless beef trim products imported from Canada that may be contaminated with E. coli O157:H7...
